class.name: AST
class.preview: RULES: - ASTs are reusable. Don't store scope/instance refs there - Parent knows about children, not the other way around.

class.name: Watch
class.preview: angular/angular-watch_group.Watch corresponds to an individual watch registration on the watchGrp.

class.name: WatchGroup
class.preview: angular/angular-watch_group.WatchGroup is a logical grouping of a set of watches. angular/angular-watch_group.WatchGroups are organized into a hierarchical tree parent-children configuration. angular/angular-watch_group.WatchGroup builds upon angular/change_detection.ChangeDetector and adds expression (field chains as in a.b.c) support as well as support function/closure/method (function invocation as in a.b()) watching.

class.name: FunctionApply
class.preview: Extend this class if you wish to pretend to be a function, but you don't know number of arguments with which the function will get called.
